&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>Docker</category><category>redis</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ce-shi-shi-dockerzhong-duan-wu-fa-xian-shi-zhong-wen/</guid><pubDate>Sat, 30 Dec 2017 16:00:02 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Redis修改默认端口</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/redisxiu-gai-mo-ren-duan-kou/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;pre class="literal-block"&gt;
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; emacs /etc/redis/redis.conf
port 8083
bind 0.0.0.0
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; redis-server /etc/redis/redis.conf
